# Files in the repo root that should NOT be uploaded as deployed static assets.
# Cloudflare Workers/Pages reads this (gitignore syntax) when publishing assets.
# Without it, the build's node_modules/ (incl. a 119 MiB workerd binary) gets
# swept in and trips the 25 MiB per-asset limit.

node_modules
.git
.gitignore
.wrangler
.github
*.log

# Build tooling & source — not needed by the deployed static site
data
generate-data.mjs
make-og-image.mjs
og-image.svg
package.json
package-lock.json
README.md
LICENSE
.assetsignore
